variables.name: COLUMN_RANK
variables.comment:
* Rank of the data. This is an integer used for ranking the search results. This is
         * application specific.

variables.name: COLUMN_CLASS_NAME
variables.comment: * Class name associated with the data (usually a Fragment class name).

variables.name: COLUMN_ICON_RESID
variables.comment: * Icon resource ID for the data.

variables.name: COLUMN_INTENT_ACTION
variables.comment: * Intent action associated with the data.

variables.name: COLUMN_INTENT_TARGET_PACKAGE
variables.comment: * Intent target package associated with the data.

variables.name: COLUMN_INTENT_TARGET_CLASS
variables.comment: * Intent target class associated with the data.
